Description: Undetected Python version of the Playwright automation library
 Patchright is a patched version of the Playwright testing and automation
 library, designed to be undetected by bot-detection systems.
 .
 It provides the same API as Playwright for browser automation with
 Chromium, Firefox, and WebKit browsers.
 .
 After installation, run: patchright install chromium
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 library.
